rows: The indicator lamp blinks, but the battery does not charge.

- **There is dirt on the battery terminals:** Clean the terminals with a soft, dry cloth (ðŸ“– 36).
- **The battery has been charged many times:** Select **BATTERY AGE** to view the battery age; if the battery is old, replace it with a new battery (ðŸ“– 276). If the battery still fails to charge, contact your Fujifilm dealer (ðŸ“– 356).
The power supply icon is not displayed.
Confirm that **POWER SUPPLY ON/COMM OFF** is selected for **USB POWER SUPPLY/COMM SETTING** (ðŸ“– 270).
